        <abstract>
            <p>CD is working hard on variations.</p> 
<p>Asks if PHG’s bald-pate pigeon [described in <hi rend="italic">A naturalist’s sojourn in Jamaica</hi> (1851)] is a true rock-pigeon.</p> 
            <p>Can he obtain a specimen of the rabbits that have run wild, and a wild canary, and the body of any domestic or fancy pigeon which has been in the West Indies for some generations?</p>
        </abstract>
